{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/useMemo-and-useCallback","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"45aea0a6-1562-55a0-b16d-c734d228eb2c","html":"<h2 id=\"1-usememo란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-usememo%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"1 usememo란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. useMemo란?</h2>\n<p>  성능 최적화를 위하여 연산된 값을 재사용하는 기능을 가진 함수로 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 될때마다 실행되는 불필요한 연산을 방지  </p>\n<h2 id=\"2-usememo-사용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-usememo-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"2 usememo 사용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. useMemo 사용 방법</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"usememo를-사용하지-않은-경우\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usememo%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EC%9D%80-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\" aria-label=\"usememo를 사용하지 않은 경우 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useMemo를 사용하지 않은 경우</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>  <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/a2510/no_useMemo0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.166666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/8ac56/no_useMemo0.webp 240w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/d3be9/no_useMemo0.webp 480w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/e46b2/no_useMemo0.webp 960w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/a5d4d/no_useMemo0.webp 1000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/09b79/no_useMemo0.jpg 240w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/7cc5e/no_useMemo0.jpg 480w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/6a068/no_useMemo0.jpg 960w,\n/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/a2510/no_useMemo0.jpg 1000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/561228da210bdefc82630660b03f57e6/6a068/no_useMemo0.jpg\"\n            alt=\"no_useMemo\"\n            title=\"no_useMemo\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>  <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 781px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/1cf11/no_useMemo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/8ac56/no_useMemo.webp 240w,\n/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/d3be9/no_useMemo.webp 480w,\n/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/42cfc/no_useMemo.webp 781w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 781px) 100vw, 781px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/09b79/no_useMemo.jpg 240w,\n/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/7cc5e/no_useMemo.jpg 480w,\n/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/1cf11/no_useMemo.jpg 781w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 781px) 100vw, 781px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/993385fdffe78a902a956614a4838dd3/1cf11/no_useMemo.jpg\"\n            alt=\"no_useMemo\"\n            title=\"no_useMemo\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>  이렇게 변수를 정의하고, return 내에서 count값을 사용하게 되면 users에 변화가 없더라도 컴포넌트가 리렌더링 될때마다 countActiveUsers 함수가 실행되게 된다.</p>\n<p>  이러한 상태에서 useMemo를 사용해 보자.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"usememo를-사용한-경우\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usememo%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\" aria-label=\"usememo를 사용한 경우 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useMemo를 사용한 경우</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>  <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/693cc/useMemo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.583333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/8ac56/useMemo.webp 240w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/d3be9/useMemo.webp 480w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/e46b2/useMemo.webp 960w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/6257a/useMemo.webp 988w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/09b79/useMemo.jpg 240w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/7cc5e/useMemo.jpg 480w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/6a068/useMemo.jpg 960w,\n/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/693cc/useMemo.jpg 988w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/eec7da54da71520fcda14b6104ce02c7/6a068/useMemo.jpg\"\n            alt=\"useMemo\"\n            title=\"useMemo\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>  이렇게 useMemo를 사용해서 count에 countActiveUsers함수를 할당하는 경우 최초 호출 시 연산한 값을 기억(memorized)해두었다가 내용이 바뀌지 않는다면 기억해두었던 원래의 연산값을 재사용하게 된다.</p>\n<p>  <strong>✔  useRef와의 차이</strong></p>\n<p>  useRef는 단순히 특정 값을 기억한다면, useMemo는 deps가 변경되기 전까지의 값과 복잡한 함수의 return값을 보관하는 역할로 사용 </p>\n<h2 id=\"3-usecallback이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-usecallback%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"3 usecallback이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. useCallback이란?</h2>\n<p>  useMemo가 특정 value를 재사용하기 위함이라면, useCallback은 특정 함수를 새로 만들지 않고 재사용하기 위해 사용하는 Hook</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-usecallback-사용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-usecallback-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"4 usecallback 사용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. useCallback 사용 방법</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"usecallback으로-정의하고-조건을-달아준다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usecallback%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%EB%8B%AC%EC%95%84%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"usecallback으로 정의하고 조건을 달아준다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useCallback으로 정의하고 조건을 달아준다</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 763px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/7a8c4/useCallback.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.16666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/8ac56/useCallback.webp 240w,\n/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/d3be9/useCallback.webp 480w,\n/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/0c209/useCallback.webp 763w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 763px) 100vw, 763px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/09b79/useCallback.jpg 240w,\n/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/7cc5e/useCallback.jpg 480w,\n/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/7a8c4/useCallback.jpg 763w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 763px) 100vw, 763px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7bba6755bb5f6c1e04d5705117d1d18c/7a8c4/useCallback.jpg\"\n            alt=\"useCallback\"\n            title=\"useCallback\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>  useMemo와 유사하게 각 함수마다 useCallback으로 정의하고, 조건을 달아준다. 함수 안에서 사용하는 상태 혹은 props가 있으면 꼭 deps배열 안에 포함시켜야 한다. </p>\n<p>  이렇게 useCallback을 사용하여 props가 바뀌지 않았으면 VirtualDOM에 새로 렌더링하지 않게 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-react-리렌더링-줄이기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-react-%EB%A6%AC%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EC%A4%84%EC%9D%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"5 react 리렌더링 줄이기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. react 리렌더링 줄이기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>useMemo / useCallback 사용\n​- 단순히 태그 안에 {margin:10px;}와 같이 값읕 지정해 버리면 매번 다른 객체로 인시되어서 값이 바뀌지 않아도 해당 태그 부분이 리렌더링 될 수 있다. 따라서 스타일 지정 시 styled 사용해서 동일한 객체로 인식되어서 값이 바뀌었을때만 리렌더링이 일어나도록 적용해준다. </li>\n<li>\n<h4 id=\"styled-import-예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#styled-import-%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"styled import 예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>styled import 예시</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b4667eb484be8f757c6dbc98a9526689/67c18/styled.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.083333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b4667eb484be8f757c6dbc98a9526689/8ac56/styled.webp 240w,\n/static/b4667eb484be8f757c6dbc98a9526689/d3be9/styled.webp 480w,\n/static/b4667eb484be8f757c6dbc98a9526689/e46b2/styled.webp 960w,\n/static/b4667eb484be8f757c6dbc98a9526689/42749